("THE SUSPENSION TRAINER WORKOUT FOR BUILDING MASS", "https://bit.ly/2SOkyM2", "Don’t write off the benefits of the suspension trainer when it comes to putting on mass.", "Bodybuilding", "TRX System", "Set the straps of the suspension trainer to midheight and grab a handle in each hand. Squat down, until the bottoms of your thighs are past parallel, and then drive back up. From there, lean back, allowing your arms to fully extend, and then perform a body-weight row. The squat plus the row equals 1 rep.", "10 reps", "5 sets", "15 minutes", false, false),
